text: Desmiphora nigroannulata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 2002. It is known from Brazil and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora nigroannulata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 2002
